<h2>Policy</h2>
The content (or design) policies define the design properties of a component, like the components available or minimum/maximum dimensions. These are applicable to the template (and pages created with the template). Content policies can be created and selected in the template editor of the touch-optimized UI. Let's create a new policy to be able to add our custom components to the XF.
<pre class="lang:xml decode:true" title="/conf/site-com/settings/wcm/policies/content.xml">&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?&gt;
&lt;jcr:root xmlns:sling="http://sling.apache.org/jcr/sling/1.0"
&nbsp;&nbsp; xmlns:cq="http://www.day.com/jcr/cq/1.0"
&nbsp;&nbsp; xmlns:jcr="http://www.jcp.org/jcr/1.0"
&nbsp;&nbsp; xmlns:nt="http://www.jcp.org/jcr/nt/1.0"
&nbsp;&nbsp; xmlns:rep="internal"
&nbsp;&nbsp; jcr:mixinTypes="[rep:AccessControllable]"
&nbsp;&nbsp; jcr:primaryType="cq:Page"&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;wcm jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;foundation jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;components jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;responsivegrid jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;site-com-default
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; jcr:description="Default policy for layout containers"
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; jcr:title="PS Default"
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; sling:resourceType="wcm/core/components/policy/policy"
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; components="[group:Group1,group:Group2,...]"&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/site-com-default&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/responsivegrid&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/components&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/foundation&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/wcm&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;site-com jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; sling:resourceType="nt:unstructured"&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;page jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; sling:resourceType="nt:unstructured"&gt;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;experience-fragment jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
